  25:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****   ==============================================================================
  26:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****   [..]
  27:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (+) Each Exti line can be configured within this driver.
  28:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  29:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (+) Exti line can be configured in 3 different modes
  30:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Interrupt
  31:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Event
  32:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Both of them
  33:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  34:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (+) Configurable Exti lines can be configured with 3 different triggers
  35:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Rising
  36:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Falling
  37:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Both of them
  38:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  39:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (+) When set in interrupt mode, configurable Exti lines have two different
  40:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         interrupt pending registers which allow to distinguish which transition
  41:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         occurs:
  42:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Rising edge pending interrupt
  43:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Falling
  44:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  45:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (+) Exti lines 0 to 15 are linked to gpio pin number 0 to 15. Gpio port can
  46:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         be selected through multiplexer.
  47:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  48:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****                      ##### How to use this driver #####
  49:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****   ==============================================================================
  50:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****   [..]
  51:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  52:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Configure the EXTI line using HAL_EXTI_SetConfigLine().
  53:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Choose the interrupt line number by setting "Line" member from
  54:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  55:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Configure the interrupt and/or event mode using "Mode" member from
  56:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  57:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) For configurable lines, configure rising and/or falling trigger
  58:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              "Trigger" member from EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  59:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) For Exti lines linked to gpio, choose gpio port using "GPIOSel"
  60:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              member from GPIO_InitTypeDef structure.
  61:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  62:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Get current Exti configuration of a dedicated line using
  63:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         HAL_EXTI_GetConfigLine().
  64:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Provide exiting handle as parameter.
  65:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Provide pointer on EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure as second parameter.
  66:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  67:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Clear Exti configuration of a dedicated line using HAL_EXTI_ClearConfigLine().
  68:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Provide exiting handle as parameter.
  69:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  70:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Register callback to treat Exti interrupts using HAL_EXTI_RegisterCallback().
  71:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Provide exiting handle as first parameter.
  72:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Provide which callback will be registered using one value from
  73:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              EXTI_CallbackIDTypeDef.
  74:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Provide callback function pointer.
  75:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  76:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Get interrupt pending bit using HAL_EXTI_GetPending().
  77:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  78:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Clear interrupt pending bit using HAL_EXTI_ClearPending().
  79:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c **** 
  80:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Generate software interrupt using HAL_EXTI_GenerateSWI().
